title: Converse Rubber Tracks: Oh, Hello - Heliotropes
description:
Meet the four members Heliotropes who all grew up in different places, but are now collectively based in Brooklyn, NY. Growing up as part of the "MTV generation" they credit their close families and friends with influencing their individual musical tastes. Hear how the Heliotropes came up with their unique band name and what their experience was like at Converse Rubber Tracks. 
For more on Converse Rubber Tracks visit:
http://www.converse.com/rubbertracks
